  not_derived_from:
    - "lodash source"
  notes:
    - "lodash.sortedlastindex exports the _.sortedLastIndex function directly as module.exports."
    - "sortedLastIndex(array, value) uses binary search to find the highest insertion index."
    - "For duplicate values, returns the index AFTER the last occurrence."
